            <title>[THRIFT-3414] #include &lt;pwd.h&gt; in THeaderTransport.h breaks windows build</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3414</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The #include &amp;lt;pwd.h&amp;gt; in THeaderTransport.h breaks windows build, because it doesn&apos;t have a pwd.h.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When removing the header I don&apos;t see any errors neither on Windows nor on Linux (GCC).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the file is not needed at all. The attached patch removes it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
